{"tid":2225834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<真係咁憎我哋?>南丫海難8周年︱便衣警嘲祭品垃圾 譏市民做戲悼亡魂","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:37:59.000Z","uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9491e5528858ea72d0aa1a2aed1f0d66c59c6c","tid":2225834,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=b5af558b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&h=e1933378\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/</a><br />\n南丫海難8周年，「女長毛」雷玉蓮今年繼續於中環4號碼頭旁悼念死難者。悼念集會今年首次受警方阻撓，有便衣警聲稱拜祭用的紙錢是垃圾，又稱雷「做戲」、「消費意外」，並在儀式完成後向雷發告票稱違反「口罩令」。其間雷一度情緒激動，反斥警員「冇人性」，「係咪立咗國安法，連南丫海難都唔准拜？」，表明來年會繼續拜祭，希望港人出席悼念。<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n集會期間一度有多名防暴警員到場，其中一名便衣警甫到場即稱紙錢為垃圾，要求雷玉蓮終止悼念及拾回散落周圍的紙錢。雷玉蓮感不滿與警員理論，強調紙錢不是垃圾，警員則一度拉起封鎖線，並聲稱會票控雷。雷回應指不介意收告票，「如果你為咗海難告我，我心甘命抵」，要求完成拜祭。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n警方阻撓雷玉蓮拜祭南丫海難期間，有剛於碼頭落船的市民疑不滿警方做法，高聲批評警員，在場警員隨即發難，截查該名市民。現場記者上前追訪時，該名聲稱拜祭紙錢是垃圾的便衣警，疑伸腳企圖絆倒一名網媒女記者。《蘋果》記者所見，該名便衣警伸出一隻腳幾乎成「一字馬」姿勢，幸女記者反應快速，及時跳過才未有被絆倒。"},{"pid":"42491c7b98bb567148f47ca00cc9a98cd5dcc59a","tid":2225834,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f25d3e4319ad51eddf9f38bb749e8c0c6ca062a","tid":2225834,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"班狗剩係識好似小學雞咁串人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa8a197a94ff731564242300125e94c489035cd","tid":2225834,"uid":321313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a091d81cc1246ea656d94fd8ad3874011c29ae5d","tid":2225834,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4f25d3e4319ad51eddf9f38bb749e8c0c6ca062a","tid":2225834,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"班狗剩係識好似小學雞咁串人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"真係咁憎我哋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d696a5936138eef2df9d4104aff1dc11ebc8b5","tid":2225834,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f62865fb30a06276b3394c40f571e8d1a5ed949","tid":2225834,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:29:25.000Z","msg":"呢班黑警真係唔當市民係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n零同理心"},{"pid":"27f5ab953d3dab790730bac654a13e4a6fda203f","tid":2225834,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df347f18bfe816b1f8de7050ad174daae782b25","tid"